#UPDATE Fresno Police say the two victims were shot at by a suspects in another car.
@ABC30 — Nathalie Granda (@NathalieABC30) November 2, 2019Fresno police appear to be looking at this car.
@ABC30 pic.twitter.com/ctrUCQ1J3r — Nathalie Granda (@NathalieABC30) November 1, 2019Active scene on Tyler and Fisher.
Neighbors tell me they believe it was a shooting, and heard at least 4 rounds.
One victim, a man in his 30s, was grazed in the stomach, and the other was not injured.Police do not believe the shooting was gang-related.
